Google Cloud Platform(GCP):
---------------------------
*As of June 2024, Google Cloud Platform (GCP) has over 40 regions and 121 zones worldwide.Each region has 3 availability zones.\

Region-->Specific geographical location to host our resources.
Adavantages:
-----------
*High Availability
*Low Latency
*Global Footprint
*Adhere to government regulations

Zones-->we can achieve high availability with same region using zones.Every region has 3 availability zones.
*Each Zone has one or more discrete clusters(cluster means distinct physical infrastructure that is housed in data center).
*zones in an region are connected with low-latency risks

Advantage
-----------:
Increased availability and fault tolerance within the region.



